alerts.description:
There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Max. gusts: ~ 75 km/h; Wind direction: south-west

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: ~ 55 km/h; Wind direction: south-west
There is a slight risk of icy surfaces (Level 1 of 4).

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: ~ -1 °C

There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Precipitation amounts: 1-3 cm; in windward areas: < 5 cm
